edu.ncsu.csc.Galant.graph.component

Class EdgeState

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc.Galant.graph.component.EdgeState

  • public class EdgeState
extends java.lang.Object
    The state of an Edge, used akin to a frame in an animation. As the animation advances, the subsequent EdgeState is evoked to be displayed in the animation window.
    Author:
    Jason Cockrell, Ty Devries, Alex McCabe, Michael Owoc
